    <briefdescription>
<para>Lookup table with linear interpolation. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>For calibration curves, thermistor tables, transfer functions, etc. The table is a const array of (x, y) pairs, sorted by ascending x. Lookups interpolate linearly between the two nearest entries.</para>
<para>Header-only — integer math, no floating point.</para>
